  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There has been a horrific surge in Coronavirus infections and deaths in India. The health care system is extremely overwhelmed and social media is inundated with pleas for medical devices and medications.  OBLF can simply not look away during this crisis and is collaborating with health officials to  set up a 50 bedded Covid Care Center in Jigani, Bangalore. For the short term, all funds raised via this platform will be directed to the Care Center.</narrative>
